  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/28/skype-free-group-video-calls-on-desktop-and-xbox-one/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/204305e3f4505e5d118f5a4dc07a6289/200076054/xboxone1.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div>为了更好地与 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googlehangouts\">Google Hangouts</a> 竞争，微软今天做出了为所有桌面及 Xbox One 版 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/skype\">Skype</a> 用户免费提供群组视频通话功能的决定。在此之前，这项功能在上述平台都需要付费订阅才可使用，现在不用花钱，应该会吸引到更多的使用者吧。除此之外，微软还表示「再过不久」便会有更多平台享受到同样的福利，各位就好好期待一下吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/04/28/skype-free-group-video-calls-on-desktop-and-xbox-one/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://blogs.skype.com/2014/04/28/skype-loves-bringing-groups-together-with-free-group-video-calling/\" target=\"_blank\">Microsoft</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/28/skype-free-group-video-calls-on-desktop-and-xbox-one/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20876992/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/28/skype-free-group-video-calls-on-desktop-and-xbox-one/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
